{
  "stem": "5470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the first sign where you got to see that the people were not agreeing with what the Germans were doing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what could you do more?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were in occupation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Too openly you couldn't show it because then you were picked up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, that's a story that I forget, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened was, when we were at war, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the beginning of May in 1940, that actually the occupation started off on the 15th, and the war started on the 10th.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was from Indonesia, and Indonesia was still a free country, and in Indonesia all these [? christlings-- ?] we called them [? christlings-- ?] the people who were in favor of Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the party, the NSB, they have it picked up in Indonesia, because the [INAUDIBLE] they are French or with the German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a reaction in Holland after that, that for those people who were picked up in Indonesia, the Germans and those NSB-ers, they were looking for people who were related to those families in Indonesia.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was one of them, and they came up one day at the front door to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, luckily, I wasn't home at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I went under straightaway the day thereafter into the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually it was then closed by [INAUDIBLE] already at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was under for about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germans did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were picking me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was there, so that was a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was under for about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were only once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I expected them to come back the day thereafter, so I went straightaway on the-- and they never returned.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
